<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>New Comment Alert</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .email-container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border: 1px solid #dddddd;
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #4caf50;
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 24px;
    }
    .body {
      padding: 20px;
      color: #333333;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .body h2 {
      margin-top: 0;
    }
    .footer {
      background-color: #f1f1f1;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 10px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #666666;
    }
    .footer a {
      color: #4caf50;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .footer a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>New Comment Alert</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="body">
      <h2>Hello <%= noteOwner.firstName %>,</h2>
      <p>
        We wanted to let you know that <strong><%= commenter.firstName %> <%= commenter.lastName %></strong> 
        has commented on the patient note you made for <strong><%= patient.name %></strong>.
      </p>
      <blockquote style="border-left: 4px solid #4caf50; padding-left: 10px; margin: 10px 0; color: #555;">
        "<%= comment %>"
      </blockquote>
      <p>
        You can view the note and respond if necessary by logging into your account.
      </p>
      <p>
        Thank you for your attention!
      </p>
      <p>Best regards,</p>
      <p>The Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Your Institution. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p><a href="<%= institutionUrl %>">Visit our website</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
